<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bank</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-oBqDVmMz9ATKxIep9tiCxS/Z9fNfEXiDAYTujMAeBAsjFuCZSmKbSSUnQlmh/jp3" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-cuYeSxntonz0PPNlHhBs68uyIAVpIIOZZ5JqeqvYYIcEL727kskC66kF92t6Xl2V" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<body>
    <div id="navbar" class="container">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-light">
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                        <img class="logo" src="/img/logo.png" alt="">
                    </a>
                    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                        <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto container-fluid justify-content-around">
                            <li class="nav-item text-center w-25 mx-3">
                                <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item text-center w-25 mx-3">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="#services">Services</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item text-center w-25 mx-3">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="#">About us</a>
                            </li>
    
                            <!-- Conditionally render buttons based on whether user is logged in -->
                            <% if (userId) { %>
                                <li class="nav-item text-center w-25 mx-3">
                                    <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                                </li>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <li class="nav-item text-center w-25 mx-3">
                                    <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Sign in</a>
                                </li>
                                <li class="nav-item text-center w-25 mx-3">
                                    <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                                </li>
                            <% } %>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>
    

        <div id="sloganBox" class="container-fluid justify-content-center">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <span id="slogan" class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">Secure. Reliable. Here for You.</span>
                        <button id="becomeClientBtn" type="button" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Become a client right now </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6 d-flex justify-content-center"><img class="slogan-img" src="/img/slogan-img.png" alt=""></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="services" class="container">
            <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                <h2>SERVICES</h2>
                <div class="row d-flex w-100 mt-3">
                    <div class="col service-card d-flex flex-column align-items-center mx-3">
                        <h3 class="my-3">Account Services</h3>
                        <ul class="d-flex h-100 flex-column justify-content-evenly service-info">
                            <li class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="./static/img/check-icon.png" alt="" class="me-2"> <!-- Add margin-end for spacing -->
                                Personal Checking & Savings Accounts: Details on account types with example features like low fees, easy access, and basic interest rates.
                            </li>
                            <li class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="./static/img/check-icon.png" alt="" class="me-2">
                                Business Accounts: Information on options for small businesses, including potential account benefits.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col service-card d-flex flex-column align-items-center mx-3">
                        <h3 class="my-3">Loan Services</h3>
                        <ul class="d-flex h-100 flex-column justify-content-evenly service-info">
                            <li class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="./static/img/check-icon.png" alt="" class="me-2"> <!-- Add margin-end for spacing -->
                                Personal Loans: Simulated loan options, describing types, example terms, and a mock interest rate calculator.
                            </li>
                            <li class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="./static/img/check-icon.png" alt="" class="me-2">
                                Home Loans & Mortgages: A description of mortgage types with an interactive mortgage calculator.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col service-card d-flex flex-column align-items-center mx-3">
                        <h3 class="my-3">Investment Services</h3>
                        <ul class="d-flex h-100 flex-column justify-content-evenly service-info">
                            <li class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="./static/img/check-icon.png" alt="" class="me-2"> <!-- Add margin-end for spacing -->
                                Savings Plans: Example options for building savings through high-yield accounts.                            
                            </li>
                            <li class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="./static/img/check-icon.png" alt="" class="me-2">
                                Mutual Funds & Retirement Planning: Educational content on types of mutual funds or basic retirement plans, with hypothetical growth scenarios.                           
                             </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="aboutUs" class="conainer-fluid">
            <div class="container d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center">
                <h3>ABOUT US</h3>
                <p>
                    At Bank, we are committed to helping individuals and businesses achieve their financial goals with ease and confidence. With a focus on security, innovation, and customer service, Bank offers a wide range of banking solutions designed to meet the diverse needs of our community. From personal and business accounts to loan options and investment guidance, we empower our clients to manage their finances seamlessly and securely.
<br>Founded on principles of trust and reliability, we believe in the power of strong relationships and clear communication. Our dedicated team works tirelessly to deliver solutions tailored to your needs, while our secure, state-of-the-art digital banking platforms make banking more accessible than ever.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="footer" class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row d-flex"> <!-- Added text-center for center alignment -->
                <div class="col d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                    <img class="iconImg" src="/img/facebook.png" alt="">
                    <img class="iconImg" src="/img/instagram.png" alt="">
                    <img class="iconImg" src="/img/linkedin.png" alt="">
                    <img class="iconImg" src="/img/youtube.png" alt="">
                </div>
        
            </div>
            <div class="row d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pb-3">
              
